{
  "name": "RPlog_Convoy_Assault_and_Capture",
  "title": "Convoy Assault and Capture",
  "summary": "A New Republic strike force led by Raxis 'Raptor' L'ygr and his wingman Lance 'Wildman' Corbet, supported by Ranger patrol's Y-wings and A-wings and two Marine-laden dropships, ambushes an Imperial convoy of four freighters in the border regions. Aboard the corvette HIMS Visceral, Marshal Krieg launches with his wingman, the Sarian pilot Liza 'Slush' Molokai, and engages the raiders in a sprawling dogfight of taunts and daredevil maneuvers. The Y-wings methodically disable freighters with ion fire while Krieg, Raxis, Liza, and Lance trade blows through the furball, the New Republic losing fighters even as it cripples Imperial TIEs. Krieg's own fighter is ultimately disabled and recovered by the corvette's tractor beam before the Imperials jump out, leaving two freighters captured. The Marines board the disabled freighters and the New Republic claims a hard-won victory.",
